main event: Two objects with blue-green lights were observed maneuvering in the sky before disappearing at high speed.
interesting points: The sighting occurred approximately 100 yards away from the witness., The objects were noted to be around 90 degrees from the witness's position before climbing steeply., The observation lasted about 1 minute., Weather conditions were clear with bright moonlight at the time of a separate sighting in the area., The report concluded the object remains unidentified with no evidence of conventional aircraft.
witness description: The object was observed as a silent, orange-colored light approximately the size of a baseball.
